node.text:
SKINNN 💦💦💦

As you all know I’m always traveling and the @dermalogica Smart Response Serum helps my skin adapt to the different environments! SmartResponse technology helps stop skin damage before it starts – using four smart actives which, when triggered, hydrate, brighten, soothe, and address the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles in response to skin’s changing needs #DermalogicaPartner #SmartResponseSerum
